        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer935491478" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8787268927786626989">Usha, an Indian girl is forced into an arranged marriage then widowed. She escapes a widow&apos;s burning and flees to Africa to find the father who has abandoned her.<br/><br/>Set against a backdrop of 19th century Indian Indenture, the shipment of Indians to work on white-owned sugar plantations in Natal, Paul Haston&apos;s critically acclaimed novel is a story of hope and tragic drama.<br/><br/>Usha is a young woman facing many injustices by her culture, family and society. She endures much and marches on but finds the em</span>
  <span id="freeText8787268927786626989" style="display:none">Usha, an Indian girl is forced into an arranged marriage then widowed. She escapes a widow's burning and flees to Africa to find the father who has abandoned her.<br /><br />Set against a backdrop of 19th century Indian Indenture, the shipment of Indians to work on white-owned sugar plantations in Natal, Paul Haston's critically acclaimed novel is a story of hope and tragic drama.<br /><br />Usha is a young woman facing many injustices by her culture, family and society. She endures much and marches on but finds the emotional toll unbearable. Just when we believe Usha will receive all she deserves another trial and tribulation tests her yet again. Her strength, courage and tenacity is put to the test, the outcome will surprise you as it did me. <br /><br />Rising of a Dead Moon is a story rich in culture, human indignities and slavery. Undertones of romance and military are present as well. If you find the points cited unappealing than Paul Haston's book isn't a suggested read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8787268927786626989" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


